==English==

===Etymology===
Gained popularity following its frequent use in the 1990s comedy TV series [[w:Father Ted|Father Ted]]; appears to be much older &mdash; might have originated from the Irish ''[[feic]]'', "look here".

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɛk|-ɛk]]

===Verb===
'''feck'''
# (''Irish slang'') To [[steal]].<sup>1</sup>

===Interjection===
'''feck!'''
(''euphemistic'') [[Fuck]]!

